= Advisable


== DESCRIPTION

Add before, after and around advice in dynamic fashion.
This is an expirmental foray into a generic AOP mixin.


== FEATURES/ISSUES

* Extends Method class and makes them 1st class objects.


== SYNOPSIS

  ... to be done ...


== REQUIREMENTS

* Ruby Facets


== HOW TO INSTALL

Describe your installation procedure here.

To install with RubyGems simply open a console and type:

  gem install advisable

Old-school site installation requires Ruby Setup (gem install setup).
See http://proutils.github.com/setup for information.


